2. 事务B修改事务A读取的记录,提交事务B
3. 事务A再读取,又会生成一个read view,此时它可以看到事务B修改的记录值,所以read committed会出现不可重复读</p></body></html></richcontent></node><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_6521a6d22f53" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="repeatable&amp;nbsp;read&amp;nbsp;&#22312;&#31532;&#19968;&#27425;&#35835;&#21462;&#25968;&#25454;&#26102;&#25165;&#29983;&#25104;read&amp;nbsp;view"><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head><body><p>1. 事务A读取一些记录,未提交 (生成read view)
2. 事务B修改事务A读取的记录,提交事务B
3. 因为repeatable read只在第一次读取数据时才生成read view,此时事务A再读取,使用的还是步骤1那个read view,所以可见性和步骤1时一样,步骤2中事务B修改的,看不到</p></body></html></richcontent><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_8078a63e2640" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="repeatable read&#21487;&#20197;&#31105;&#27490;&#32477;&#22823;&#37096;&#20998;&#24187;&#35835;&#65292; &#21482;&#26377;&#37096;&#20998;&#24187;&#35835;&#19981;&#33021;&#31105;&#27490;"><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head><body><p>- 事务A读取一些记录,未提交 (生成read view)
- 事务B添加满足事务A刚刚读取搜索条件的记录,提交事务B
- 事务A修改刚刚事务B添加的记录
- 事务A再次读  ,发生幻读,因为事务A修改事务B添加的记录时会把记录对应的trx_id改为事务A的事务id,所以再次读时,根据read view规则这些修改的值也可见了</p></body></html></richcontent></node></node><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_660b79f9362d" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="seriablizable &#21152;&#38145;"></node></node><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_5058f6e7557d" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#22914;&#26524;read view&#19981;&#20877;&#35775;&#38382;&#29256;&#26412;&#38142;&#20013;undo&#26085;&#24535;&#24050;&#32463;delete mark&#30340;&#35760;&#24405;&#65292;&#23601;&#21487;&#20197;&#25191;&#34892;purge&#30495;&#27491;&#21024;&#38500;&#35760;&#24405;"></node></node><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_b58088788c7b" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#38145;"><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_9b75bc52082b" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#38145;&#30340;&#21010;&#20998;"><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_5c8c23da30a0" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#38145;&#30340;&#20316;&#29992;&#22495;"><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_265f6b352804b781" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#20840;&#23616;&#38145;"><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_2c5c006b47384c1e" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#38145;&#25968;&#25454;&#24211;&#23454;&#20363;"></node><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_33d30d18514a0516" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#25968;&#25454;&#21516;&#27493;"></node></node><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_b544211a1dd4b790" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#34920;&#38145;"><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_545342d1f06ae8cd" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#34920;X&#38145;"></node><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_73448aae5a0bd902" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#34920;S&#38145;"></node><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_b620694c1b34438a" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#20803;&#25968;&#25454;&#25152;&amp;nbsp;"><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_2e07842e2729993d" MODIFIED="1709652756325" TEXT="&#20462;&#25913;&#34920;&#32467;&#26500;"></node></node></node><node CREATED="1709652756325" ID="ID_fc82355b6b9ec926